<HEAD>CBS News' Ferrugia Takes Denver Channel 4 Co-Anchor Job</HEAD>
<DATELINE>DENVER (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   CBS News ``West 57th'' correspondent John Ferrugia
will become co-anchor on Denver's KCNC Channel 4 ``Colorado Evening
News'' beginning Sept. 11.
   Ferrugia, 38, signed a multiyear contract with KCNC, reportedly
worth about $200,000 a year.
   Ferrugia told The Denver Post he and his wife, Mona, decided to
