was on the road. I calculated I was working a 70-hour week,
including about 17 hours a week on an airplane or to and from an
airplane. At a certain point you have to evaluate what's important.
... My first priority has always been family,'' Ferrugia said.
   His past assignments included the White House and Justice
Department beats, the civil war in Lebanon, martial law in Poland
and American political conventions.
