<SECOND>PM-Wall Street 2pm,0286</SECOND>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Stock prices staged a modest advance today,
rebounding from Tuesday's setback.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials climbed 7.97 to 2,649.09
by 2 p.m. on Wall Street.
   Gainers outnumbered losers by about 8 to 7 in nationwide trading
of New York Stock Exchange-listed issues, with 749 up, 646 down and
